    "body": [
      {
        "_key": "d8a9e0b1c2d3",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "f80bd57a-a08d-45c4-a91d-5c64eec1626b",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "看護助手の仕事は、医療現場での経験がなくても挑戦できる魅力的な職種です。しかし、数ある求人の中から、本当に未経験でも安心して働ける職場を見つけるのは難しいと感じるかもしれません。"
          },
          {
            "_key": "3c1abe60-985f-4056-be0c-0f562e07409e",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "\n"
          },
          {
            "_key": "d3f9bbfb-d1be-487d-81c5-3f053503884f",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ""
          },
          {
            "_key": "6a64240a-f7e8-4051-8270-b8d1ae36131d",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "\n"
          },
          {
            "_key": "e2963ff1-8fd3-4539-a5f9-bf19d57e1dc4",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ""
          },
          {
            "_key": "11b4f9f3-10fa-4bf1-ae2f-a0eac2fedf21",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "\n"
          },
          {
            "_key": "e6793aa5-5e7d-42d2-95f8-cb967f5a59cf",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "この記事では、未経験OKの看護助手求人を選ぶ際の重要なコツを解説します。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "b2c3d4e5f6a1",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "036c2377-a7f4-48aa-9a5c-152cd562bcbe",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "未経験OK求人の見極め方"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "c6c10775-9737-406e-8773-136e8f385fe9",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "reference-span-label-e9bf377a-d202-47a8-abc7-ecad3104566e",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "参考: "
          },
          {
            "_key": "reference-span-link-6ebd3979-7610-41cb-bc95-8534f5eb8129",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "link-eccf7689-f6cc-4bd6-bee0-9bb1e5b515a4"
            ],
            "text": "厚生労働省 看護職員需給分科会"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "link-eccf7689-f6cc-4bd6-bee0-9bb1e5b515a4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/seisakunitsuite/bunya/0000188411.html"
          }
        ],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "c3d4e5f6a1b2",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "d9a9eea5-516d-42ce-a188-048b0d4cc14d",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "「未経験者歓迎」の言葉だけを鵜呑みにしない"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h3"
      },
      {
        "_key": "g1h2i3j4k5l6",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "6116d788-6707-4525-9071-9a70170b8d36",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "求人票に「未経験者歓迎」と書かれていても、実際に教育体制が整っているかは別問題です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "h2i3j4k5l6g1",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "315c0f9b-a07d-4cac-9223-115891579cdf",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "研修制度の有無と内容：入職後の研修が充実しているか、具体的な内容が明記されているかを確認しましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "reference-e45a5f2b-6eba-4ab8-8fc5-3cd7686fb4ca",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "reference-span-label-aec32791-ec70-4912-a93e-0a39d121f8ca",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "参考: "
          },
          {
            "_key": "reference-span-link-28643a4b-77ec-4fda-b181-46f644e909a9",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "link-1e9c959a-cd47-4aea-b3f6-43881b14f982"
            ],
            "text": "日本看護協会 看護補助者の離職状況レポート"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "link-1e9c959a-cd47-4aea-b3f6-43881b14f982",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://www.nurse.or.jp/home/assets/20231005_nl01.pdf?utm_source=chatgpt.com"
          }
        ],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "i3j4k5l6g1h2",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "40946f39-5ba7-4f97-ac1e-0d234b0a0e9b",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "教育体制の充実度：OJT（On-the-Job Training）がしっかりしているか、先輩が丁寧に指導してくれる環境かどうかが重要です。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "followup-af0a806b-75cc-4f2a-ba8b-a98428e8f51b",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "text-a6e22045-6bd0-47a0-9e7a-d160150d163c",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "これらを参考に、自分に合った方法を見つけてください。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "reference-ad77eeb1-81bc-4165-a9bd-8603628f6c5b",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "reference-span-label-8f1ccbea-61dc-4d3c-902f-2105d9793909",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "参考: "
          },
          {
            "_key": "reference-span-link-c6b53615-77da-4471-9677-3f3cbc853f8c",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "link-b9083d76-02e7-4810-85aa-1d6d97e5cf43"
            ],
            "text": "厚生労働省 看護師等学校養成所卒業生就業状況調査"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "link-b9083d76-02e7-4810-85aa-1d6d97e5cf43",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/list/100-1.html"
          }
        ],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "j4k5l6g1h2i3",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "bba86bda-974e-48b3-b160-59ae08bb6b70",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "職場の雰囲気やサポート体制を重視する"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h3"
      },
      {
        "_key": "k5l6g1h2i3j4",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "cbfcd53c-2a19-43bc-a2a8-ec277e4b8505",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "未経験だからこそ、困った時に助けてくれる環境が大切です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "l6g1h2i3j4k5",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "bc27d45d-8382-408b-8fca-3290cb23e886",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "病院見学：可能であれば、実際に足を運び、職場の雰囲気やスタッフの様子を自分の目で確認しましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "reference-4b18b49c-2dc0-43d6-a502-939be0b17694",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "reference-span-label-e24b40d6-6a19-4dd2-b801-eb137874e7a2",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "参考: "
          },
          {
            "_key": "reference-span-link-8488c722-624d-4809-b453-4849f4d79ad4",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "link-ea1ff46b-3efe-40bc-a35a-dfa77656f773"
            ],
            "text": "日本看護協会 看護サービス提供体制のあり方"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "link-ea1ff46b-3efe-40bc-a35a-dfa77656f773",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://www.nurse.or.jp/home/publication/pdf/guideline/way_of_nursing_service.pdf?utm_source=chatgpt.com"
          }
        ],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "m1n2o3p4q5r6",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "bad187bb-e886-4ceb-be8f-be44c549a1a2",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "先輩看護助手の声：求人サイトや病院のウェブサイトで、実際に働いている人の声が掲載されているかチェックしましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "section-closing-52a2ce60-7ee1-411f-9414-ed44549369e6",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "section-closing-span-b032381c-2074-4f7e-873d-edda6d5aeef9",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "未経験OK求人の見極め方では、看護師と連携しながら無理のない範囲で進めることが大切です。気になる点はその都度共有し、安全第一で取り組みましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "reference-73df2c95-c8a9-4a5c-b0a6-f58b1586df40",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "reference-span-label-682f9f8e-7823-4321-9815-cf0adf760056",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "参考: "
          },
          {
            "_key": "reference-span-link-35aeea64-95aa-4b76-a56b-77bcf5506448",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "link-895fe51f-38c1-4a6d-b913-ef39ad3c71b5"
            ],
            "text": "厚生労働省 医療施設調査"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "link-895fe51f-38c1-4a6d-b913-ef39ad3c71b5",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/list/79-1.html"
          }
        ],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "a2b3c4d5e6f1",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "0acd9906-0e0d-4107-879f-7617dc15dfaa",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "未経験者が安心して働ける職場の特徴"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "l17pjfjnb0n7",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "fvuibmjv1qcj",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "求人票の「未経験者歓迎」という言葉だけでなく、その背景にある教育体制やサポート体制が整っているかどうかが、安心して働ける職場を見つけるための鍵となります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "n2o3p4q5r6m1",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "061063f6-40b7-4f7c-a776-1d9e7a348239",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "丁寧なOJT（On-the-Job Training）がある：実践を通じて、一つずつ業務を教えてもらえる環境は非常に重要です。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "o1p2q3r4s5t6",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "6c7e55f5-817a-43ce-bb15-0a5debda17f4",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "質問しやすい環境、相談しやすい先輩がいる：困った時にすぐに聞ける雰囲気があるかどうかも大切です。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "p2q3r4s5t6o1",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "0c781479-252d-49f7-a9da-6504f75887bc",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "業務マニュアルが整備されている：いつでも確認できるマニュアルがあると、安心して業務に取り組めます。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "q3r4s5t6o1p2",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "362f3f72-104e-4e44-875d-fdd060450f03",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "チームワークが良好で、助け合う文化がある：医療現場はチームプレーです。お互いをサポートし合う文化がある職場は働きやすいでしょう。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "section-closing-46917dc3-5ae9-4639-999a-2c8746aab3e7",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "section-closing-span-ff736e7e-2a28-4296-9921-0b567b91c99a",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "未経験者が安心して働ける職場の特徴では、看護師と連携しながら無理のない範囲で進めることが大切です。気になる点はその都度共有し、安全第一で取り組みましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "r4s5t6o1p2q3",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "03e345b0-7db4-4844-b82b-dacaa2bd28a6",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "求人情報でチェックすべきポイント"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "j2ws5bmjqn18",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "c7onmnly8los",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "求人票には多くの情報が書かれていますが、特に未経験者が注目すべきポイントがいくつかあります。これらの情報をしっかり確認し、自分に合った職場かを見極めましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "s5t6o1p2q3r4",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "b0d89dbf-fcaa-456a-81d9-47f35e0237a5",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "研修制度の有無と内容：具体的な研修期間や内容が明記されているか。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "t6o1p2q3r4s5",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "eb708c4e-4d69-4174-9038-b6563946dad9",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "資格取得支援制度の有無：働きながら資格を取りたい場合に重要です。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "u1v2w3x4y5z6",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "718d6106-c973-4cb4-a9ef-381c3a357467",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "勤務形態：夜勤の有無、残業時間、シフトの柔軟性など。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "v2w3x4y5z6u1",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "3eb124df-7527-47f7-bde5-00fda16b534e",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "給与・福利厚生：初任給だけでなく、昇給や賞与、各種手当も確認しましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "followup-09114754-4b4e-47d3-acba-a72eb1a1a9aa",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "text-bdb47ab0-fd58-42db-83a4-70a00ab26975",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "上記の点に注意しながら、無理なく取り組んでいきましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "w3x4y5z6u1v2",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "5d25d201-e493-4826-87ae-b841d7d0d473",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "転職エージェントの活用もおすすめ"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "x4y5z6u1v2w3",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "3f1ffdcb-e8cf-4782-a476-f6aca0e4806b",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "未経験からの転職では、転職エージェントのサポートが非常に役立ちます。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "y5z6u1v2w3x4",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "46ee2c97-e4ae-4ee7-abee-326247212fcb",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "未経験者向けの求人情報を提供してくれる。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "z6u1v2w3x4y5",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "44ae376e-f21f-4ab0-8c85-7a00b4b0d44e",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "職場の内部情報に詳しい場合がある。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "a3b4c5d6e7f1",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "fc265e3c-12b2-4167-979b-d136019076d3",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "履歴書添削や面接対策のサポートを受けられる。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
